snippet: The computer networking giant overcame a challenging environment for corporate spending. Its stock rose 5 percent after hours.
abstract: Cisco Systems delivers quarterly results that slight surpass analysts' forecasts; fiscal fourth-quarter profit was $1.9 billion, up 56 percent from year-ago quarter; revenue was $11.7 billion, up 4 percent.
lead_paragraph: The computer networking giant overcame a challenging environment for corporate spending. Its stock rose 5 percent after hours.

headline.seo: Cisco Revenue and Profit Exceed Forecasts
headline.main: Cisco Revenue and Profit Exceed Forecasts as Orders in Asia Stay Strong
headline.print_headline: Cisco Revenue and Profit Exceed Forecasts as Orders in Asia Stay Strong
